---
// Componente de cita minimalista - sin section wrapper
---

<div class="quote-component">
  <blockquote class="quote-content">
    <p class="quote-line-1">
      La inteligencia artificial no es el futuro de tu empresa.
    </p>
    <p class="quote-line-2">
      Es su presente.
    </p>
    <p class="quote-description">
      Cada día que pasa sin implementarla, tu competencia automatiza procesos, mejora decisiones y 
      transforma la experiencia de sus clientes.
    </p>
    <footer class="quote-footer">
      <p class="quote-cta">El momento de actuar es ahora</p>
      <p class="quote-context">TRANSFORMACIÓN DIGITAL CON IA</p>
    </footer>
  </blockquote>
</div>

<style>
  .quote-component {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-content {
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-line-1 {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #e5e5e5;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
  }

  .quote-line-2 {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa 0%, #a855f7 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  .quote-description {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #9ca3af;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.4s;
  }

  .quote-footer {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-cta {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #02aa6d;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.6s;
  }

  .quote-context {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #6b7280;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.8s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quote-component {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .quote-line-1,
    .quote-line-2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .quote-description {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .quote-cta {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .quote-component {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .quote-line-1,
    .quote-line-2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .quote-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .quote-context {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
    }
  }
</style>
